      "writtenOn": "2019-09-26T23:39:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t know about the transport level.\n\nI\u0027m cheating here and setting a high limit just so we can test that this actually works, since I suspect we\u0027re the only ones who are sending files \u003e5MB right now.  Once we\u0027ve verified that this actually works, I definitely agree with lowering the limit if the transport doesn\u0027t do it.\n\nPedantically\n\nM \u003d 10^6\nMi \u003d 2^20\n\nhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Binary_prefix\n\nI don\u0027t care if LUCI wants to stick with with the \"incorrect\" binary prefixes though.",
